commit message: Create CHANGELOG.md
Update README.md
Rewrite RouteTimes from scratch to use Dijkstra algorithm
Implemented making of route by using precomputed values from shortest path search
Fixed bug with routing, in the case multiple drivings are available
Fixed bug: starting point was not included in route
Fixed the case when route doesn't exist
Performance optimizations of path finding
Removed public fields fromStart, toEnd from RouteTimes class, replacing them with getTime methods
Split graph class to separate graph operations and conversion from nodes to indices
Moved creating of shortest path from RouteTimes into Graph
Refactoring RouteTimes.Node class
Simplified path finding by restricting it to only one start node and one end node by adding extra nodes to each station
Added logging of exception, which had been silently ignored
Fixed crashes that were caused by multiple threads accessing RouteTimes object, fixed bugs that happened after changing of waiting time and available transportations
Minor fixes of readme
Fixed displaying of time for unreachable stations and fixed building of routes in the case some transports are not active
Fixed appearing of ghosting route when maps of different transportations are switched
Fixed appearing of ghosting route when end station is not reachable

Revert 'ClassCastException in SharedPreferencesImpl.getInt()'

This reverts commit 80c29e82cd92d11006385725dff5a978d3a4e6b2.

Revert 'Revert 'ClassCastException in SharedPreferencesImpl.getInt()''

This reverts commit e58c9a0d56b48e48fa242b8b4b877c05da39fc94.

Merge pull request #5 from asdzxcasd/master

Fixed issues with long computing time of routes
Test release 0.0.15
Active transports are not disabled while switching schemes in the case route start is selected
Upgrade Android Studio to v2.0

Fixing list of active transports while maps are switched
